  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Other Important Information Childrens Privacy We do not knowingly collect any personal information from children under the age of 13 without parental consent unless permitted by law If we learn that a child under the age of 13 has provided us with personal information we will delete it in accordance with applicable law</evidence>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

